meta.name: Azaphenacenes
meta.description:
This map was generated using KPCovR with
α=0.65 and 2 principal components, using electronic mobility and DFT level
crystal energy as the biaising properties, and SOAP structural descriptors.

The crystal structures and electronic mobility come from crystal structures
prediction of 28 azaphenacenes-like molecules.
references: *Structure-Property Maps with Kernel Principal Covariates Regression* B. A. Helfrecht, R. K. Cersonsky, G. Fraux, M. Ceriotti, https://arxiv.org/abs/2002.05076

*Large-Scale Computational Screening of Molecular Organic Semiconductors Using Crystal Structure Prediction*, J. Yang, S. De, J. E. Campbell, S. Li, M. Ceriotti, and G. M. Day, Chem. Mater. 2018, 30, 13, 4361-4371. https://doi.org/10.1021/acs.chemmater.8b01621
